Hi Dabing:

I'm not sure you'd need sapply or lappy. Perhaps something like this would work? (NB: untested code)

P_diss <- function(X,Y,V,S){
	result<-pmin(z*(X^(1/3))*(S-Y/V),X)
	result[(X<=0)|(S<Y/V)]<-0

	return(result)
}

Cheers,
Daniel

